Developmental modality

This one fits your Audience Alignment work.

Instead of saying:

“This is for children.”

You could encode:

developmental_modality:
  comprehend: age 8
  regulate: age 10
  appreciate: age 14
  create: age 18

Different developmental milestones for different interactions.

⸻

Modal stacks

Even more interesting is that modalities compose.

Example:

Observed
Possible
Urgent
Reversible
Low confidence

versus

Simulated
Necessary
Long-term
Irreversible
High confidence

The words might be similar, but the cognitive posture is completely different.

